Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.84,0:00:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Aphrodite!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.88,0:00:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你看起来好匆忙，发生什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.40,0:00:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,小调岛的三重唱被大调岛的战士捉了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.00,0:00:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.56,0:00:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我看，这两个应该是Baritone 和Bassdrum
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.36,0:00:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.52,0:00:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我是大调岛的三剑客。。。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.64,0:00:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Falsettol
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.24,0:00:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也是！BARRITONE....BASSDRUM
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.64,0:00:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我们中计了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.24,0:01:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Mephisto!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.92,0:01:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,爱人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.84,0:01:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,APHRODITE!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.00,0:01:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.48,0:01:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,APHRODITE!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.52,0:03:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,还差那么一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.44,0:03:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我们只能等待乐器的完成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.08,0:03:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,所以现在的我们必须阻止不幸曲子完成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.48,0:03:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.56,0:03:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有G-Clefs 【音部记号】
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.36,0:03:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,光之美少女，你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.80,0:03:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Falsettol
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.44,0:03:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sniffle!!!x2 .....不幸曲子。。完成！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.60,0:03:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,给你们看看好东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.72,0:03:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.28,0:03:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.36,0:03:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,亚子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.32,0:03:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,伤感的话就在这结束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.60,0:03:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你要对我妈妈怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,放了她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.16,0:03:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你要她回来，那么，把你们的变身器叫出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.08,0:03:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,变身器？！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.32,0:03:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.72,0:04:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你们不答应
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.00,0:04:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.36,0:04:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,巴斯朵拉！巴利頓！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.04,0:04:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你们邪恶的心灵不是在之前已经消失了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.20,0:04:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你们没觉得自责吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.84,0:04:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,对，你们到最后是在伤害你们自己
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.68,0:04:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,NOISE 是在利用你们收集绝望的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.44,0:04:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,难道你们都没关系吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.24,0:04:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,住嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.84,0:04:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,快来小调岛，你们没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.28,0:04:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.08,0:04:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.96,0:04:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.04,0:04:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.88,0:04:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,亚子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.76,0:04:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,没事情的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.84,0:04:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我回去救妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.96,0:05:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你会？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.48,0:05:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.72,0:05:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是我造成这一切
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.24,0:05:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己会去小调岛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.68,0:05:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我们要确定愛芙羅黛蒂现在是安全的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.60,0:05:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,还有我们要考虑交出我们的变身器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.56,0:05:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,艾莲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.68,0:05:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.40,0:05:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是对变身器里面的G CLEFS吸引
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.08,0:05:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他们去了它们，不幸曲子将完成，NOISEye也将会复活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.52,0:05:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这不能让它发生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.84,0:05:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,一起去小调岛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.64,0:05:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会找办法救APHRODITE,不会牺牲我们的变身器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.68,0:05:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.80,0:06:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,加油啊，传说中的光之美少女战士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.44,0:06:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,她们来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.96,0:06:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.16,0:06:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,亚子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.16,0:06:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你们放心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.40,0:06:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,别将你们的变身器交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.96,0:06:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,快回去人类世界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.28,0:06:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好适合你啊，大调岛女王
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.92,0:06:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,但这我都不管
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.68,0:06:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你们都有带变身器吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.08,0:06:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.60,0:07:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.56,0:07:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,住口
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.80,0:07:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,NOISE 能分辨出真伪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.16,0:07:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,将它们交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.64,0:07:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,快释放Aphrodite先
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.40,0:07:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你们没权利和我谈条件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.96,0:07:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你伤害APHRODITE
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.44,0:07:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就破坏G-CLEFS
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.60,0:07:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也变不成光之美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.36,0:07:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,但你的不幸曲子将不会完成
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.48,0:07:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,NOISE说它拿到变身器后，就会释放APHRODITE
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.72,0:07:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这到底是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.20,0:08:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,现在变身器就在你我之间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.20,0:08:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,放了APHRODITE然后在那拿了变身器吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.40,0:08:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想进行肮脏交易的话。。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.88,0:08:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就会取回变身器而变成光之美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.48,0:08:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,然后再打倒你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.56,0:08:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,NOISE说他同意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.96,0:08:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,正如我想的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.36,0:08:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,弗賽托！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.16,0:08:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的。。。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.28,0:09:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,BASSDRUM!BARITONE!杀了APHRODITE!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,快动手！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.20,0:09:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.60,0:09:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.88,0:09:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我的爱人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.48,0:09:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,MEPHISTO!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.60,0:09:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,哈咪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.40,0:09:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.28,0:09:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,剩下的就交给你们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.32,0:09:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,大家，现在打败NOISE
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.08,0:09:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.80,0:09:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,LET'S PLAY! PRECURE MODULATIONS
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.44,0:11:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,指尖彈奏的是狂野的曲調！旋律天使（Cure Melody）！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.36,0:11:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,指尖彈奏的是柔和的曲調！節奏天使（Cure Rhythm）！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.36,0:11:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,指尖彈出的是靈魂的曲調！節拍天使（Cure Beat）！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.88,0:11:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,指尖彈出的是女神的曲調！繆思天使（Cure Muse）！」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.28,0:11:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,共鸣吧，我们的组曲音乐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.64,0:11:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,组曲光之美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.92,0:12:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,巴黎顿!巴斯多啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.60,0:12:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,那两个就交给你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.96,0:12:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我赐予你们NOISE大人的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.12,0:12:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,终于是我展现我的真正力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.20,0:12:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,吃这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.96,0:12:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,快避开
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.16,0:12:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,何等力量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.92,0:12:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,大家，就是时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.36,0:12:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.72,0:12:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,米莉，来这吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.04,0:13:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,法利，来这吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.56,0:13:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,索利，来这吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.68,0:13:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,实利，来这吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.72,0:13:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,出来吧，TONE RING
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.88,0:13:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,实利，闪耀曲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.96,0:13:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,光之美少女 音樂圓舞曲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.92,0:13:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,光之美少女 心靈搖滾曲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.08,0:13:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,光之美少女 閃爍洗禮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.80,0:13:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,三拍子 1･2･3･Finale!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.80,0:14:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.24,0:14:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.76,0:14:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,亚子，大家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.16,0:14:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手！巴黎顿，巴斯多啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.00,0:14:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,他们变成怪售后就再也听不到我说什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.12,0:14:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,接招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.32,0:15:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.44,0:15:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你止住了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.04,0:15:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会变成这样都是因为我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.24,0:15:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我没告诉过你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.84,0:15:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我。。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.48,0:15:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我被NOISE控制了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.72,0:15:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,大调岛的三剑客
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.88,0:15:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是我把他们变成小调岛三重唱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.00,0:15:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我。。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.08,0:15:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我能变回来是因为亚子的大家的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.36,0:15:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.48,0:15:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他们并没有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.68,0:16:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我对他们做过的。。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.60,0:16:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.24,0:16:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,巴斯多啦！巴黎顿！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.72,0:16:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,把梅菲时特解决掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.36,0:16:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸，快逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.48,0:16:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我做过的事！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.08,0:16:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.88,0:16:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.48,0:16:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,巴斯多啦！巴黎顿！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.32,0:16:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我犯下的罪！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.48,0:16:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,让NOISE邪恶的力量传入我身上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.96,0:17:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这是。。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.72,0:17:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我们恢复正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.20,0:17:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的，发生了什么事？！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.52,0:17:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该连同我自己消灭这邪恶的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.12,0:17:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,怎可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.40,0:17:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你这样做，你会。。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.40,0:17:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但是，这是唯一的办法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.80,0:17:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好好照顾亚子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.04,0:17:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,邪恶的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.24,0:17:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.00,0:17:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,随着这神圣的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.80,0:17:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.32,0:17:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.84,0:17:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,巴黎顿！巴斯多啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.36,0:18:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,恢复你们原来的本性吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.84,0:18:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.52,0:18:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.20,0:18:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.56,0:18:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,牺牲自己来对付邪恶力量，。。真是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.20,0:18:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然对梅菲时特嘲笑。。。他用生命对抗恶势力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.96,0:18:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对无法原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.80,0:18:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，如果我们没打败NOISE,和平就不会来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.84,0:18:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,大家，再来一次！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.80,0:18:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.16,0:18:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你们还不懂吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.44,0:18:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你们是打不到我的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.96,0:19:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,旋律，节奏，节拍，缪斯！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.48,0:19:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,大家！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.76,0:19:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,旋律你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.12,0:19:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,光之美少女。。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.60,0:19:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.64,0:19:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,光之美少女和梅菲时特玩完了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.48,0:19:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,巴斯多啦！巴黎顿！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.60,0:19:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,快解决掉APHRODITE!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.12,0:19:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.44,0:19:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.40,0:19:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了，快恢复你们以前在大调岛的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.28,0:19:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你们还在那边干嘛？！快下手！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.28,0:19:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,巴斯多啦。。。巴黎顿。。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.16,0:19:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.28,0:19:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,APHRODITE!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.44,0:19:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,给你这个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.44,0:19:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,巴黎顿！巴斯多啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.08,0:20:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.64,0:20:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,保护愛芙羅黛蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.12,0:20:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你们可恶！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.36,0:20:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,背叛我的就要死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.28,0:20:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,就是，喊吧，真是超棒的音乐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.68,0:20:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,巴斯多啦，巴黎顿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.28,0:20:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.16,0:20:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.04,0:20:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.20,0:20:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.84,0:20:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,愛芙羅黛蒂，对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.36,0:21:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,要将你们的调音器交出来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.52,0:21:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,世界将遭遇什么，你们都知道吧。。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.92,0:21:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.20,0:21:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,但我不能再忍受我的朋友们受伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.32,0:21:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我朋友们在受伤害，怎样才是快乐的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.04,0:21:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,朋友。。。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.44,0:21:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我们吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.32,0:21:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,终于
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.00,0:21:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,终于不幸曲子完成了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.60,0:23:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,*本字幕由kentkenneth翻译*\N谢谢观赏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.76,0:23:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我们再也变不了光之美少女了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.48,0:23:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,传说中的音符变成了负向音调
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.96,0:23:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,NOISE也变成巨大化了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.84,0:23:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,加音町的人民全部变成了石头
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.28,0:23:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我们该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.36,0:23:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.56,0:23:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我们怎能放心呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.16,0:23:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,因为是圣诞节嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.72,0:24:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,组曲光之美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.08,0:24:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,DO.RE.RA.DO.奇迹出现在神圣的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.80,0:24:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我们和平就在你心里产生共鸣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.40,0:24:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,*本字幕由kentkenneth翻译*
